The dataset Crime is gathered from Houston Texas Police crime report from January to August 2010. The data is cleaned and arranged so that only more serious crimes (murder, Rape, robbery and aggravated assault) are considered.The data is geocoded with longitude and latitude information with Google Maps and mapped using the Leaflet map widget.
